Limits

This would not stop everything.

It would be weaker against:
	•	server-side hidden models
	•	loyalty-only ecosystems
	•	dynamic pricing blended with inventory
	•	marketplaces where seller and platform signals are fused

But even then, it can still create observability, and observability changes behavior.

